organic.title: Able Kids Foundation: Home
organic.snippet: Welcome to Able Kids Foundation. Able Kids Foundation specializes in the diagnosis and management of central auditory processing disorder (CAPD).

organic.title: The Able Kids Foundation Difference
organic.snippet: Able Kids Foundation is a global leader in the field of central auditory processing disorder and provides unparalleled levels of CAPD service.

organic.title: Our Staff - Able Kids Foundation
organic.snippet: Fort Collins, CO 80525. Hours of Operation. Monday - Thursday: 8am - 5pm. Contact. (970) 226-2253 · info@ablekidsfoundation.org. © 2024 Able Kids Foundation.

organic.title: Planning Your Appointment - Able Kids Foundation
organic.snippet: Appointments are available at 9 am and 1 pm, Monday through Thursday at our office. Remote testing is not available.

organic.title: Contact Us - Able Kids Foundation
organic.snippet: Contact the Able Kids Foundation to learn more about how we can help you or someone you love manage Central Auditory Processing Disorder.
